  "title": "Outlet Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p>Position: <strong>Outlet Sales Manager</strong></p><p>Salary: <strong>SGD3,000 – SGD4,000 per month (Basic, excluding commissions & incentives)</strong></p><p><br /><strong>About De Beaute:</strong><br /><br />High-End established brand in Beauty, Slimming & TCM Wellness Spa.<br />De Beaute is a high-end, established name in Singapore’s beauty and spa wellness industry, case-trusted and approved, renowned for delivering exceptional services and customer satisfaction. Join our passionate team and be part of an award-winning brand that sets the standard in beauty and wellness.</p><p><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>- Lead, motivate, and manage the sales team to achieve monthly and annual sales targets</p><p>- Develop and implement effective sales strategies and in-house promotions</p><p>- Build and maintain strong relationships with new and existing clients</p><p>- Provide professional consultation and excellent customer service on De Beaute’s range of beauty and wellness services</p><p>- Conduct training, coaching, and performance evaluations for the sales team</p><p>- Analyze sales data, monitor KPIs, and prepare regular performance reports for management review</p><p>- Collaborate closely with marketing and operations teams to ensure successful campaign execution and customer engagement<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>- Proven experience with a track record in sales as a Sales Manager or similar role, preferably in the beauty, slimming, spa, wellness, or retail industry</p><p>- Strong leadership, people management, and team-building skills</p><p>- Excellent communication, interpersonal, and presentation abilities</p><p>- Results-driven, self-motivated, and able to work independently in a fast-paced environment</p><p>- Good knowledge of beauty and wellness products/services is a strong advantage</p><p>- Ability to analyze data and make strategic decisions<br /></p><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><p>-Sundays and Public Holidays off.</p><p>- Attractive basic salary with high commissions and incentives</p><p>- Career advancement and professional development opportunities</p><p>- Staff discounts on all beauty and spa services</p><p>- Supportive, dynamic, and collaborative team environment</p><p>- Recognition and rewards for outstanding performance<br /><br /><strong>Working Hours :</strong><br />Mon - Fri : 10.30 am to 8.30 pm<br />Sat : 10 am to 6 pm<br />Closed on Fri & PH<br /><br />Interested candidates, please contact us via WhatsApp at <strong>8133 3030</strong>. Initial interviews will be conducted via video call, followed by an in-person office interview.</p>",
